high_descs: Walk across the room to the bed.
Pick up the cell phone on the bed.
Turn towards the nightstand with the red credit card.
Put the cell phone in the bowl on the nightstand.
Pick up the bowl with the cell phone in it.
Turn, go towards the door, and take a right past the bed to the desk.
Set the bowl with the cell phone in it down on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a cell phone inside on the desk.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the middle of the room and turn left towards the bed.
Pick up the cell phone on the bed.
Turn right towards the night stand.
Place the cell phone in the clear bowl on the night stand.
Pick up the bowl from the night stand.
Turn around and head towards the dresser on your right.
Place the bowl on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Place the cell phone on the desk into a bowl to transfer to the desk.

high_descs: Walk straight then turn to the bed on your left
Pick up the phone on the bed in between the two laptop
Turn to you right and walk towards the table
Put the phone in the bowl on the left side of the table
Pick up the bowl on the table
Turn around to your right and walk past the bed
Face the table at the end of the bed and put the bow  on the table in between other things
anns.task_desc: Travel the bowl with phone from one table to the other table
